(x,y,z)
(1,1,1)
 \theta = \arctan\left(\frac yx\right)\\ \phi = \arctan\left(\frac {\sqrt{x^2+y^2}}z\right) 
 \theta = \arctan\left(\frac 11\right)=45˚\\ \phi = \arctan\left(\frac {\sqrt{2}}1\right) \approx 55˚ 
